  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Pic Blanc is offered on a half board basis and meals will be taken in the restaurant 'Le Rif Briant'.</p>
<p>Each morning fuel up for a day on the slopes at the continental buffet breakfast which has a variety of sweet and savoury options, as well as additional hot options. </p>
<p>Enjoy a four course evening meals with a choice of menu and waiter service each evening, the menu blends traditional dishes with regional favourites.</p>
<p>Christmas and New Year Gala dinners included.</p>
<p>Earlier meal times for children are available from 7:15pm and children's food available in the buffet.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
